Domain Requirements :
            The functional and non-functional requirements that arise from the particular business 
domain in which the system will operate.

 Example:
      E-Commerce Domain (e.g., Amazon)

Domain Requirements:
           * System must allow users to add/remove products from the cart.
           * Discounts and tax calculations must follow regional laws.
           * Orders should support multiple payment methods (UPI, Credit Card, Wallet).

Test Cases Example:

          Test Case ID	    Test Scenario             	                   Expected Result

          TC-001            Verify product added to                        Product appears in cart with 
                            cart is displayed correctly                    correct price

                         
